The paper deals with image quality assessment, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of structural-similarity index (SSIM) and histogram-based entropy and cross entropy suggest that the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories. The use of regression module for inferring quality score suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
